! High-symmetry k-path for rutile 2x2x1 supercell (tetragonal)
! Verify with SeeK-path: https://seekpath.materialscloud.org
! Path: Gamma -> M -> X -> Gamma -> Z -> R -> A -> Z
K_POINTS crystal_b
  8
  0.000  0.000  0.000   50   ! Gamma
  0.500  0.500  0.000   40   ! M
  0.500  0.000  0.000   30   ! X
  0.000  0.000  0.000   50   ! Gamma
  0.000  0.000  0.500   30   ! Z
  0.500  0.500  0.500   40   ! R
  0.500  0.000  0.500   30   ! A
  0.000  0.000  0.500    1   ! Z

HUBBARD (ortho-atomic)
  U Sn-4d 4.0
  U O-2p  0.0
